	     (REPLACE (SETQ MODE (QUOTE REPLACE)))
	     (ERASE (SETQ MODE (QUOTE ERASE)))
	     (1 (SETQ BRUSH 1))
	     (2 (SETQ BRUSH 2))
	     (3 (SETQ BRUSH 3))
