		      (ACE.MT.SCRY.SEQY (fetch (REGION BOTTOM) of TEMPREGION))
		      NIL NIL (QUOTE INPUT)
		      (QUOTE ERASE))
	    (BITBLT NEWBM 0 0 ABITMAP (ACE.MT.SCRX.SEQX (fetch (REGION LEFT) of TEMPREGION))
